social_posts.post_text:
For the second consecutive season, I will be supporting @smiletrain for #mycausemycleats 

Smile Train is the world’s largest cleft-focused organization, with a sustainable and local model of supporting surgery and other forms of essential care for cleft patients. Over the last 21 years, Smile Train has supported safe and quality cleft care for 1.5+ million children.

This cause is close to my heart because I was born with a cleft lip, and without proper care, I might not be where I am today. These cleats will be worn in our game this Sunday vs. the Giants and can be bid on using the link in my bio.

Had a great day in DC cheering on @washingtonspirit ⚽️

shoutout @win26d for making our day an incredible one!

baby bates coming this fall 👼🏼

James 1:17 ✨ we’ve prayed for you little one!
Year 3 and still getting dropped off at work by the wife and pups 🫡
our lives just got a heck of a lot sweeter 🤍 we got to welcome our sweet girl on the evening of her daddys birthday and we feel beyond blessed to be her parents
